{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1773742776,"nonce":"h2vt4zeuRiXAEP8Cr1Z01X/o2TU=","title":"Add automated table of contents generation for markdown files","message":"README.md and AGENTS.md are growing and need tables of contents. Manually maintaining them is error-prone.\n\nInstall `doctoc` as a dev dependency and wire it up:\n\n1. `pnpm add --save-exact --save-dev doctoc`\n2. Add a `toc` script to package.json: `doctoc --update-only README.md AGENTS.md`\n3. Consider adding a pre-commit hook (no hook framework exists yet, so evaluate husky/lefthook or a simple git hook)\n4. Add doctoc markers to README.md and AGENTS.md\n5. Run it to generate the initial TOCs","files":null}]}